            [kee-frame.core :as k]
            [personal-website.db :as db]
						[personal-website.events :as events]
						[personal-website.views :as views]
						[personal-website.config :as config]))


(def routes [["/" :homepage]

             ["/who-i-am" :who-i-am]
             ["/accomplishments" :accomplishments]

             ;["/phsyics/:id" :physics]

(defn init []
